text.tspan: Based on the expert assessments and index by V-Dem, weighted by countries' populations. It combines
information on voting rights, the freedom and fairness of elections, freedoms of association and
expression, as well as the extent to which the protection of rights, access to power, and distribution of
resources is equal. It ranges from 0 to 1 (most democratic).
Data source: OWID based on V-Dem (v13); HYDE (2017); Gapminder (2022); UN (2022)
